export const clockColors: { [key: string]: string } = {
  colorWhenUsedForHoursAndMinutes:      'rgb(101, 199, 97)',
  colorWhenUsedForHours :               'rgb(57, 80, 2)',
  colorWhenUsedForMinutes:              'rgb(50, 116, 49)',
  colorWhenNotUsed:                     'rgb(64, 161, 87)',
  clockBackGroundColorArrayStartColor:  'rgb(50, 116, 49)',
  clockBackGroundColorArrayEndColor:    'rgb(64, 161, 87)',
  secondsCounterArrayStartColor:        'rgb(101, 199, 97)',
  secondsCounterArrayEndColor:          'rgb(64, 161, 87)'
}
